      <title>Codex는 `--full-auto`, Claude Code는 `--permission-mode auto`가 좋은 이유</title>
      <link>https://gyuha.com/post/2026/04/2026-04-29-codex-full-auto-claude-auto-safety-balance/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0900</pubDate>
